---
title: Rosemary Pork Medallions with Roasted Cauliflower and Watercress
description: Christmas feasts can sometimes feel like Groundhog Day, with the same recipes repeated year after year. Cauliflower cheese is a great side for a Christmas roast, but in this recipe André has given it a modern twist that will add new flavour and flair to your festive menu. Enjoy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/rosemary-pork-medallions-wk52-3ad3a54a.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/rosemary-pork-medallions-wk52-a9a3d931.pdf
